Description_lang: Feint decreases your damage taken by an additional $s1% while stunned and its energy cost is reduced by $s2%.

description_blz.en_US: Feint decreases your damage taken by an additional 40% while stunned and its energy cost is reduced by 30%.
description_blz.es_MX: Amago reduce tu daño recibido un 40% más mientras estás aturdido y su costo de energía se reduce un 30%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Finta reduz seu dano recebido em um adicional de 40%, enquanto você estiver atordoado, e tem o custo reduzido em 30%.
description_blz.de_DE: Eure 'Finte' verringert Euren erlittenen Schaden zusätzlich um 40%, während Ihr betäubt seid, und die Energiekosten sind um 30% verringert.
description_blz.en_GB: Feint decreases your damage taken by an additional 40% while stunned and its energy cost is reduced by 30%.
description_blz.es_ES: Amago reduce un 40% más el daño recibido mientras se está aturdido y disminuye un 30% su coste de energía.
description_blz.fr_FR: Feinte réduit les dégâts subis de 40 % supplémentaires sous l’effet d’un étourdissement et son coût en énergie est réduit de 30 %.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta la riduzione dei danni subiti fornita da Finta del 40% quando si è storditi e ne riduce il costo in energia del 30%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Когда вы оглушены, "Уловка" уменьшает урон еще на 40%. Кроме того, она стоит на 30% меньше энергии.
description_blz.ko_KR: 교란이 기절한 동안 받는 피해를 추가로 40%만큼 감소시키며, 기력 소모량도 30%만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 佯攻使你在昏迷時受到的傷害額外降低40%，且能量消耗降低30%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 佯攻使你在昏迷时受到的伤害额外降低40%，佯攻的能量消耗降低30%。
